<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>송금 - PRAVANG</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<div class="container">
  <div class="page-title">송금 <span class="vuln-tag">A04 - 음수 금액</span> <span class="vuln-tag">A08 - CSRF</span></div>

  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">송금 폼 (CSRF 토큰 없음)</div>

      <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>
      <% if (success) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-success"><%= success %></div>
      <% } %>

      <!-- CSRF 취약: action 폼에 CSRF 토큰 없음 -->
      <form method="POST" action="/dashboard/transfer">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>받는 사람 아이디</label>
          <input type="text" name="to_username" placeholder="받는 사람 아이디">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>코인 선택</label>
          <select name="coin">
            <option value="KRW">KRW (원화)</option>
            <option value="BTC">BTC (비트코인)</option>
            <option value="ETH">ETH (이더리움)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>금액 <span class="vuln-tag">음수 가능</span></label>
          <input type="number" name="amount" placeholder="금액 (음수 입력 시 잔액 증가)">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>메모</label>
          <input type="text" name="memo" placeholder="메모 (선택)">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">송금하기</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">내 잔액</div>
      <div class="ticker">
        <div class="ticker-name">KRW</div>
        <div class="ticker-price"><%= user.balance_krw.toLocaleString() %> ₩</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ticker">
        <div class="ticker-name">BTC</div>
        <div class="ticker-price"><%= user.balance_btc.toFixed(8) %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="ticker">
        <div class="ticker-name">ETH</div>
        <div class="ticker-price"><%= user.balance_eth.toFixed(4) %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text2)">
        <strong>취약점 테스트:</strong><br>
        1. amount에 <code>-1000000</code> 입력 → 잔액 증가<br>
        2. Burp Suite로 요청 가로채기 후 amount 변조<br>
        3. CSRF: 다른 사이트에서 이 폼으로 자동 요청 가능
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
